@startuml
!theme plain

actor "Operateur" as Op
participant "Frontend
:3000" as Frontend
participant "Gateway
:4000" as Gateway
participant "Incident
Service :4004" as Incident
participant "Auth
Service :4001" as Auth
participant "Notification
Service :4005" as Notif
participant "MySQL
:3309" as DB

== Declarer un incident ==
Op -> Frontend : Remplir formulaire
Frontend -> Gateway : declareIncident(input)
Gateway -> Incident : mutation
Incident -> Auth : verify token (me query)
Auth --> Incident : user data
Incident -> DB : INSERT INTO incidents
DB --> Incident : incident created
Incident -> Notif : sendNotification
Notif --> Incident : notification sent
Incident --> Gateway : Incident
Gateway --> Frontend : Incident
Frontend --> Op : Confirmation

== Mettre a jour statut ==
Op -> Frontend : Changer statut
Frontend -> Gateway : updateIncidentStatus(id, status)
Gateway -> Incident : mutation
Incident -> Auth : verify token
Auth --> Incident : user data
Incident -> DB : UPDATE incidents SET status
DB --> Incident : updated
Incident -> Notif : sendNotification (status update)
Notif --> Incident : sent
Incident --> Gateway : Incident
Gateway --> Frontend : Incident
Frontend --> Op : Statut mis a jour

@enduml
